quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  52,24,Àwọn ọmọ-ọ̀dọ̀ wọn yó sì máa lọ bọ̀ láààrin wọn. (Wọ́n) dà bí àlúùúlù àfipamọ́
  52,25,"Apá kan wọn yóò dojú kọ apá kan, wọn yó sì máa bèèrè ọ̀rọ̀ lọ́wọ́ ara wọn"
  52,26,"Wọn yóò sọ pé: \"Dájúdájú tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀ àwa jẹ́ olùpáyà láààrin àwọn ènìyàn wa"
  52,27,Ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu ṣàánú wa. Ó sì là wá níbi ìyà Iná
  52,28,"Dájúdájú àwa máa ń pè É tẹ́lẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Olóore, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  52,29,"Nítorí náà, ṣèrántí. Ìwọ kì í ṣe adábigba tàbí wèrè lórí ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa rẹ"
  52,30,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: \"Eléwì kan tí à ń retí ikú rẹ̀ ni"
  52,31,"Sọ pé: \"Ẹ máa retí. Dájúdájú èmi náà wà pẹ̀lú yín nínú àwọn olùretí"
  52,32,Tàbí ọpọlọ wọn ń pa wọ́n láṣẹ èyí ni? Tàbí ìjọ alákọyọ ni wọ́n ni
  52,33,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: \"Ó dá (al-Ƙur’ān) hun fúnra rẹ̀ ni.\" Rárá o, wọn kò gbàgbọ́ ni"
  52,34,Kí àwọn náà mú ọ̀rọ̀ kan bí irú rẹ̀ wá tí wọ́n bá jẹ́ olódodo
  52,35,Tàbí wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá wọn láì sí Aṣẹ̀dá? Tàbí àwọn ni wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá ara wọn ni
  52,36,"Tàbí àwọn ni wọ́n ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀? Rárá o, wọn kò màmọ̀ dájú ni"
  52,37,Tàbí lọ́dọ̀ wọn ni àwọn àpótí ọrọ̀ Olúwa rẹ wà? Tàbí àwọn ni olùborí
  52,38,Tàbí wọ́n ní àkàbà tí wọ́n ń fi gbọ́rọ̀ (nínú sánmọ̀ ni)? Kí olùgbọ́rọ̀ wọn mú ẹ̀rí pọ́nńbélé wá
  52,39,"Tàbí àwọn ọmọbìnrin ni tiRẹ̀, àwọn ọmọkùnrin sì ni tiyín"
  52,40,"Tàbí ò ń bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan lọ́dọ̀ wọn, ni gbèsè fi wọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rùn"
  52,41,"Tàbí ìmọ̀ ìkọ̀kọ̀ wà lọ́dọ̀ wọn, tí wọ́n sì ń kọ ọ́ sílẹ̀"
  52,42,"Tàbí wọ́n ń gbèrò ète kan ni? Nígbà náà, àwọn t’ó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, àwọn l’ó máa f’orí kó ète"
  52,43,Tàbí wọ́n ní ọlọ́hun kan lẹ́yìn Allāhu ni? Mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu tayọ n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń fi ṣẹbọ sí I
  52,44,"Tí wọ́n bá sì rí apá kan nínú sánmọ̀ t’ó ya lúlẹ̀, wọ́n á wí pé: \"Ẹ̀ṣújò rẹgẹdẹ ni (wọn kò níí gbàgbọ́)"
  52,45,"Nítorí náà, fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ títí wọn yóò fi bá ọjọ́ wọn tí wọn máa pa wọ́n sínú rẹ̀ pàdé"
  52,46,Ọjọ́ tí ète wọn kò níí fi kiní kan rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀. A ò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́
  52,47,"Àti pé dájúdájú ìyà kan ń bẹ fún àwọn t’ó ṣàbòsí yàtọ̀ sí (ìyà ọ̀run) yẹn, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀"
  52,48,"Ṣe sùúrù fún ìdájọ́ Olúwa Rẹ, dájúdájú ìwọ wà ní ojútó Wa. Kí ó sì ṣe àfọ̀mọ́ pẹ̀lú ìdúpẹ́ fún Olúwa rẹ nígbà tí ó bá ń dìde nàró (fún ìrun kíkí)"
  52,49,"Àti ní alẹ́ (nígbà tí) àwọn ìràwọ̀ bá kúrò níta tán, ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún Un"
  53,1,(Allāhu búra pẹ̀lú) ìràwọ̀ nígbà tí ó bá jábọ́
  53,2,"Ẹni yín kò ṣìnà, kò sì sọnù"
  53,3,Àti pé kò níí sọ̀rọ̀ ìfẹ́-inú
  53,4,Kò níí sọ ohun kan tayọ ìmísí tí A fi ránṣẹ́ sí i
  53,5,"Alágbára (ìyẹn, mọlāika Jibrīl) l’ó kọ́ ọ ní ìmọ̀ (al-Ƙur’ān)"
  53,6,"Ó ní àlàáfíà t’ó péye. Nítorí náà, ó dúró wámúwámú"
  53,7,nígbà tí ó wà nínú òfurufú lókè pátápátá
  53,8,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó sún mọ́ (Ànábì). Ó sì sọ̀kalẹ̀ (tọ̀ ọ́ wá)"
  53,9,"(Àlàfo ààrin àwọn méjèèjì) sì tó ìwọ̀n ọrún ọfà méjì, tàbí kí ó kéré (sí ìyẹn)"
  53,10,Allāhu sì fún ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀ ní ìmísí t’Ó fún un
  53,11,Ọkàn (Ànábì) kò parọ́ ohun t’ó rí
  53,12,Ṣé ẹ óò jà á níyàn nípa ohun t’ó rí ni
  53,13,Àti pé dájúdájú ó rí i nígbà kejì Allāhu (subhānahu wa ta'ālā) ni ó rí bí ó tilẹ̀ jẹ́ pé igun yìí fi kún un pé ọkàn l’ó fi rí Allāhu bíi ọ̀rọ̀ tí ó tọ̀dọ̀ Ọmọ ‘Abbās (rọdiyallāhu 'anhu) wá pé “Ànábì (sollalāhu 'alayhi wa sallam) fi ọkàn rẹ̀ rí Allāhu ni.” Ìyẹn ni pé
  53,14,níbi igi sidirah al-Muntahā
  53,15,nítòsí rẹ̀ ni Ọgbà Ibùgbé (gbére) wà
  53,16,(Rántí) nígbà tí ohun t’ó bo igi Sidirah bò ó mọ́lẹ̀
  53,17,"Ojú (Ànábì) kò yẹ̀, kò sì tayọ ẹnu-àlà"
  53,18,"Dájúdájú ó rí nínú àwọn àmì Olúwa rẹ̀, t’ó tóbi jùlọ"
  53,19,Ẹ sọ fún mi nípa òrìṣà Lāt àti òrìṣà ‘Uzzā
  53,20,"àti Mọnāh, òrìṣà kẹta mìíràn"
  53,21,"Ṣé ọmọkùnrin ni tiyín, ọmọbìnrin sì ni tiRẹ̀"
  53,22,Ìpín àbòsí nìyẹn nígbà náà
  53,23,(Àwọn orúkọ òrìṣà wọ̀nyẹn) kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe àwọn orúkọ kan tí ẹ̀yin àti àwọn bàbá yín fi sọ (àwọn òrìṣà yín fúnra yín). Allāhu kò sì sọ ẹ̀rí ọ̀rọ̀ kan kalẹ̀ nípa rẹ̀. Wọn kò sì tẹ̀lé kiní kan bí kò ṣe àròsọ àti ohun tí ẹ̀mí (wọn) ń fẹ́. Ìmọ̀nà kúkú ti dé bá wọn láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wọn
  53,24,Tàbí ti ènìyàn ni n̄ǹkan t’ó bá ń fẹ́
  53,25,Ti Allāhu sì ni ọ̀run àti ayé